rComments: MOST TERRIBLE PROF. I would never take a class with him again. He RUSHES through his lectures and is absolutely confusing. Refuses to answer questions over e-mail and thinks he's top ____ because he has an MBA.

Love this prof! very helpful, approachable & kind to every student. Replies to emails quickly. Very useful sample exam questions.. His talking speed is a little too fast but understandable. Warning:know the materials inside out or you won't have enough time to finish the exam. overall great Prof!

Very nice professor - extremely helpful, approachable and clear on explaining concepts. Most important, he cares about students. He prepares you well for the exams by giving you a lot of questions to practice. His exams are not easy, but very fair. I strongly recommend people taking his course. You will definitely learn a lot from his course.
